08/18/80	module.compin

Syntax:  .ifi module "module name"


Function:
This macro begins new command, active function, or subroutine descrip-
tion.


Macro action:
1) ejects the pending page, if any.
2) generates a 14pt.  Helvetica Bold Roman (Black) flush outside index
   slug from "module name".
3) emits a level 1 TOC entry for "module name".
4) sets "module name" in 12pt.  Helvetica Bold Roman flush left to the
   page.


Notes:
Also see slug_off.compin.info.

(END)
